data.description: HIGHEST & BEST DUE TODAY (4/28) by 7:30.  This Ranch style home is situated in the prime location of Pipersville 10 minutes from the heart of Doylestown. One floor living boasting not only lovely charm but also access to prestigious schools. The residence offers the perfect blend of convenience & education for discerning buyers seeking the utmost in quality & prestige. Inside you will find a large family room with updated flooring & neutral decor. Galley kitchen with plenty of cabinet & work space. Glass door leads you to the sunny rear deck! Large master bedroom offers a walk in closet & on suite full bath. Two additional bedrooms & modernized full bath complete the main floor. Laundry room is conveniently located on the main floor. Finished basement provides additional square footage to be used as a flex space & full bathroom for guests or extended family. The unique charm & beauty of this location makes this community an exceptional place to call home. It boasts breathtaking natural landscapes, vibrant cultural offerings, & welcoming community spirit that sets it apart from the rest. Beyond its natural splendor, Pipersville offers an abundance of recreational activities for outdoor enthusiasts, from hiking, kayaking, fishing & biking trails to water sports & wildlife watching. Our thriving Doylestown area is alive with charming shops, delicious eateries, & cultural attractions, museums, castles providing endless opportunities for entertainment.e.
